  <div class="block-3">
    <div class="inner-block" id="responsibilities">
      <section class="responsibilities_for_ministerial_role responsibilities" id="responsibilities_for_ministerial_role_2350">
        <h1>Responsibilities</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Responsibilities include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Industrial Strategy</li>
  <li>small business and enterprise (including access to finance)</li>
  <li>consumer and competition (including competition law)</li>
  <li>labour markets</li>
  <li>postal affairs (including Royal Mail)</li>
  <li>corporate governance</li>
  <li>insolvency</li>
  <li>retail sector</li>
  <li>cross-government work on loneliness</li>
</ul>

<p>The minister also has temporary responsibility for the following areas:</p>

<ul>
  <li>professional services</li>
</ul>

</div>
</section>
        <section class="current-role-holder" id="current-role-holder">
          <h1>Current role holder: <span class="name">Kelly  Tolhurst MP</span>
</h1>
          <div class="govspeak">
<p>Kelly Tolhurst was appointed  Parliamentary Under Secretary of State at the Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy on 19 July 2018.</p>
</div>
          <div class="read-more">
            <a href="/government/people/kelly-tolhurst">More about this person</a>
          </div>
        </section>

